---
/**
 * rest-api/0007 · Figure 5 — If-Match optimistic concurrency: client reads ETag
 * "v7" and sends If-Match: "v7" on PUT; if still "v7" the write succeeds (new
 * "v8"), if it changed to "v8" the server returns 412 Precondition Failed.
 *
 * Copied VERBATIM from the source HTML (figure + svg + figcaption). Lives as an
 * .astro component for the kebab-case-SVG reason. Markers (#arw, #arwG, #arwR)
 * come from the source's global hidden <svg>, inlined here in a local <defs>,
 * fills/ids verbatim.
 */
---

<figure>
    <svg
        viewBox="0 0 640 190"
        role="img"
        aria-label="Optimistic concurrency: client GETs a resource with ETag v7, sends If-Match v7 on PUT; if the resource is still v7 the write succeeds, if it changed to v8 the server returns 412 Precondition Failed"
    >
        <defs>
            <marker
                id="arw"
                viewBox="0 0 10 10"
                refX="8.5"
                refY="5"
                markerWidth="7"
                markerHeight="7"
                orient="auto-start-reverse"
                ><path d="M0,0 L10,5 L0,10 z" fill="#6b675f"></path></marker
            >
            <marker
                id="arwG"
                viewBox="0 0 10 10"
                refX="8.5"
                refY="5"
                markerWidth="7"
                markerHeight="7"
                orient="auto-start-reverse"
                ><path d="M0,0 L10,5 L0,10 z" fill="#2f5d3a"></path></marker
            >
            <marker
                id="arwR"
                viewBox="0 0 10 10"
                refX="8.5"
                refY="5"
                markerWidth="7"
                markerHeight="7"
                orient="auto-start-reverse"
                ><path d="M0,0 L10,5 L0,10 z" fill="#9a2417"></path></marker
            >
        </defs>
        <g font-family="ui-sans-serif,system-ui,sans-serif">
            <text
                x="320"
                y="18"
                text-anchor="middle"
                font-size="12"
                font-weight="700"
                fill="#111110">IF-MATCH — REJECT THE WRITE THAT WOULD CLOBBER</text
            >
            <rect
                x="14"
                y="80"
                width="150"
                height="56"
                rx="9"
                fill="#f1eee2"
                stroke="#7a1f12"
                stroke-width="1.5"></rect>
            <text
                x="89"
                y="104"
                text-anchor="middle"
                font-size="12"
                font-weight="700"
                fill="#7a1f12">Client</text
            >
            <text x="89" y="121" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9" fill="#6b675f"
                >read ETag "v7"</text
            >
            <line x1="164" y1="108" x2="232" y2="108" stroke="#6b675f" marker-end="url(#arw)"
            ></line>
            <text x="198" y="100" text-anchor="middle" font-size="8.5" fill="#6b675f"
                >PUT · If-Match: "v7"</text
            >
            <rect x="234" y="80" width="140" height="56" rx="9" fill="#fff" stroke="#d8d4c8"></rect>
            <text x="304" y="105" text-anchor="middle" font-size="12" font-weight="700">Server</text
            >
            <text x="304" y="122" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9" fill="#6b675f"
                >current ETag = ?</text
            >
            <rect
                x="440"
                y="20"
                width="192"
                height="52"
                rx="9"
                fill="#eef5ee"
                stroke="#2f5d3a"
                stroke-width="1.5"></rect>
            <text
                x="536"
                y="40"
                text-anchor="middle"
                font-size="11"
                font-weight="700"
                fill="#2f5d3a">still "v7" → 200 OK</text
            >
            <text x="536" y="56" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9" fill="#244a2e"
                >write applied · new ETag "v8"</text
            >
            <rect x="440" y="118" width="192" height="58" rx="9" fill="#f7ecea" stroke="#9a2417"
            ></rect>
            <text
                x="536"
                y="139"
                text-anchor="middle"
                font-size="11"
                font-weight="700"
                fill="#9a2417">now "v8" → 412</text
            >
            <text x="536" y="155" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9" fill="#7a2218"
                >Precondition Failed · rejected</text
            >
            <text x="536" y="168" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9" fill="#7a2218"
                >client must re-fetch &amp; reconcile</text
            >
            <path
                d="M 374 96 C 400 64, 415 54, 440 48"
                fill="none"
                stroke="#2f5d3a"
                marker-end="url(#arwG)"></path>
            <path
                d="M 374 120 C 400 138, 415 144, 440 147"
                fill="none"
                stroke="#9a2417"
                marker-end="url(#arwR)"></path>
        </g>
    </svg>
    <figcaption>
        If the resource changed since the client read it, its ETag no longer matches and the server
        returns <code>412 Precondition Failed</code>. <code>If-None-Match: *</code> does the dual job
        for creation — fail if it already exists, giving a race-free create-only.
    </figcaption>
</figure>
